{"tid":2513984,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新股IPO】京東物流 苦主討論區 1","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:37:21.000Z","uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"094af6a21ef4a523e3d843b4ec6dcf34ee2c6ff2","tid":2513984,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"由京東集團分拆的京東物流通過上市聆訊，市傳最快本月招股及上市，估值或達到400億美元，集資30億至40億美元。<br />\n<br />\n根據京東物流初步招股文件顯示，去年蝕逾40億元人民幣，前年蝕超過22億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n期內，收入733.7億元人民幣，按年升47.2%。<br />\n<br />\n不過按照非國際財務報告準則計算，去年經調整盈利約17億元人民幣，前年虧損9.24億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n公司預期，今年度虧損淨額將會顯著增加，因為可轉換及可贖回優先股公允價值變動；疫情相關的政府支持減少，令毛利率下跌； 行政、銷售及市場推廣等開支增加。"},{"pid":"6f618c5657629c59074153a419e5469f347df1af","tid":2513984,"uid":364443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"近排啲支那股好多都爆晒發 唔知呢隻抽唔抽得過"},{"pid":"e203449cb19aad900b1b3f5ee125cb29c1334d84","tid":2513984,"uid":104361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:28:28.000Z","msg":"抽唔抽好"},{"pid":"cf4c29f655e9f5ee746ecae7bd49737c1be0d9b2","tid":2513984,"uid":128594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"all in"},{"pid":"71eb49b1cfc4baeca79b8b473992f50c0f4194b8","tid":2513984,"uid":74094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"呢隻可唔可以用美股京東嘅價錢計得出值唔值得抽？"},{"pid":"a59404469e3812594c57f6b5d53adf764471e786","tid":2513984,"uid":335400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"又係中丐  不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d25b0c84684bc20b6865b580dfe2d80b103635","tid":2513984,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"400億不了<br />\n同順豐差唔多貴"},{"pid":"28545fecbafd0fc4fe